node.text: My moms nephew passed away on Tuesday and they said he had been fine the day before and that day he passed. It was so sudden I’m still in denial it happened💔 my heart goes out to her family...may she be resting in peace.🙏🏼

58-year-old Salha Mesbee is the youngest patient in Singapore to die from Covid-19. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Her eldest child, Ms Siti Noraisah Ali, said that a week before the death, a doctor told her over the phone that her mother was free of the coronavirus. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
"Mama was confirmed free of Covid-19. Unfortunately, her body was unable to hold on any longer," said Ms Noraisah, 37. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
#linkinbio to read more.⁣⁣
My condolences to you and family 🙏🙏take care
🙏🙏🙏 rest in peace. My deepest condolences to the family.
